794. terrestria is not a mere epithet but=quia terrestria sunt. lacunis, sc. maris.

795. linquitur: impers. Of the four elements one, fire, can have no claim, and Lucr. has dismissed the claim of two others; the only remaining hypothesis is that earth is the general mother.
